title="Alex Nelson">Alex Nelson</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Let <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\alpha \in \Bbbk ]]></fr:tex>, let <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\Bbbk ]]></fr:tex> be a field over <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {F}]]></fr:tex>. Then <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\alpha ]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link
type="local"
href="nt-000T.xml"
addr="nt-000T"
title="Algebraic Element">algebraic</fr:link> over <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {F}]]></fr:tex> if and only if <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {F}(\alpha ) / \mathbb {F}]]></fr:tex> is a <fr:link
type="local"
href="nt-000J.xml"
addr="nt-000J"
title="Degree of extension">finite extension</fr:link>.</fr:p>
 
   
